{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/notes/urban-outfitters-typography-goof/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Urban Outfitters, ya typography dun goofed again","date":"2011-05-08T00:00:00.000Z","date_pretty":"May 8th, 2011","date_from_now":"9 years ago","last_modified_at":null,"last_modified_at_from_now":null,"path":"/notes/urban-outfitters-typography-goof/","author":null,"excerpt":"Glad to see improvements in the May 2011 Urban Outfitters catalog. Especially since I took a few issues with their typography last month.","tags":["design"],"image":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"aspectRatio":1.9927536231884058,"src":"/static/5173a1f986f93a413612065a137126a0/a2a79/UO-may11-feature.jpg","srcSet":"/static/5173a1f986f93a413612065a137126a0/6e883/UO-may11-feature.jpg 275w,\n/static/5173a1f986f93a413612065a137126a0/a09ef/UO-may11-feature.jpg 550w,\n/static/5173a1f986f93a413612065a137126a0/a2a79/UO-may11-feature.jpg 1024w","sizes":"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px"},"fixed":{"src":"/static/5173a1f986f93a413612065a137126a0/a2a79/UO-may11-feature.jpg","height":512,"width":1024}}},"toc":true,"comments":null,"comments_locked":null,"hide_meta":null},"id":"77caba9a-2ed3-57b5-85de-ba342cc7d883","html":"<p>Glad to see improvements in the May 2011 Urban Outfitters catalog. Especially since I took <a href=\"/notes/typography-urban-outfitters/\">a few issues with the typography</a> and other design choices last month.</p>\n<h2 id=\"a-step-in-the-right-direction\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#a-step-in-the-right-direction\" aria-label=\"a step in the right direction permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>A step in the right direction</h2>\n<p>I was shocked to see product copy that was almost legible and set in a serif typeface instead of a sans (<a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20111111003402/http://www.p22.com/products/underground.html\">P22 Underground</a>). Plus they even made a half effort to number blocks of text with corresponding photographs on the page (see below for example). Although it would have been nice if they actually captioned the photographs so I don’t have to think as much.</p>\n<figure>\n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; background-color: var(--input-background-color); max-width: 900px;\">\n      <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 63.272727272727266%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image lazyload\" alt=\"Urban Outfitters May 2011 serifs and italics\" title=\"Urban Outfitters May 2011 serifs and italics\" data-src=\"/static/683547231f15af489430f31585326c12/062c0/UO-MAY11-serifs-italics.jpg\" data-srcset=\"/static/683547231f15af489430f31585326c12/16841/UO-MAY11-serifs-italics.jpg 275w,\n/static/683547231f15af489430f31585326c12/50c97/UO-MAY11-serifs-italics.jpg 550w,\n/static/683547231f15af489430f31585326c12/062c0/UO-MAY11-serifs-italics.jpg 900w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n    </span>\n  <figcaption><p>The serif typeface used here is quite beautiful &#x2014; especially the ampersand glyph and italic set.</p></figcaption>\n</figure>\n<h2 id=\"how-to-ruin-good-photography-with-bad-typography\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#how-to-ruin-good-photography-with-bad-typography\" aria-label=\"how to ruin good photography with bad typography permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>How to ruin good photography with bad typography</h2>\n<p>Sullied by page spreads that are obviously more interested in making beautiful pictures than helping customers make informed buying decisions.</p>\n<figure>\n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; background-color: var(--input-background-color); max-width: 900px;\">\n      <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 62.18181818181818%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image lazyload\" alt=\"Urban Outfitters May 2011 excellent photography\" title=\"Urban Outfitters May 2011 excellent photography\" data-src=\"/static/d0a3c4985ae328209db20bd6e48064a3/062c0/UO-MAY11-photography.jpg\" data-srcset=\"/static/d0a3c4985ae328209db20bd6e48064a3/16841/UO-MAY11-photography.jpg 275w,\n/static/d0a3c4985ae328209db20bd6e48064a3/50c97/UO-MAY11-photography.jpg 550w,\n/static/d0a3c4985ae328209db20bd6e48064a3/062c0/UO-MAY11-photography.jpg 900w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n    </span>\n  <figcaption><p>It&apos;s really hard to tell what this catalog is trying to sell, beautiful photographs or clothing and accessories?</p></figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p>I’ve tired trying to discover any sort of detail on the clothing and product sold in this catalog. I mean how could I? You basically need a magnifying glass and more patience I’m willing to waste trying to sort out what price and item number goes with each photograph.</p>\n<figure>\n  <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; background-color: var(--input-background-color); max-width: 900px;\">\n      <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 24.727272727272727%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image lazyload\" alt=\"Urban Outfitters May 2011 unreadable mess\" title=\"Urban Outfitters May 2011 unreadable mess\" data-src=\"/static/d78f76814727b2972dc58a77ed4d3f4e/062c0/UO-MAY11-unreadable-mess.jpg\" data-srcset=\"/static/d78f76814727b2972dc58a77ed4d3f4e/16841/UO-MAY11-unreadable-mess.jpg 275w,\n/static/d78f76814727b2972dc58a77ed4d3f4e/50c97/UO-MAY11-unreadable-mess.jpg 550w,\n/static/d78f76814727b2972dc58a77ed4d3f4e/062c0/UO-MAY11-unreadable-mess.jpg 900w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n    </span>\n  <figcaption><p>Looks like someone&apos;s <kbd>RETURN</kbd> key is busted. Unless it was intentionally set to generate headaches&#x2026;</p></figcaption>\n</figure>","excerpt":"Glad to see improvements in the May 2011 Urban Outfitters catalog. Especially since I took a few issues with the typography and other design…","timeToRead":1,"tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/notes/urban-outfitters-typography-goof/#a-step-in-the-right-direction\">A step in the right direction</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/notes/urban-outfitters-typography-goof/#how-to-ruin-good-photography-with-bad-typography\">How to ruin good photography with bad typography</a></li>\n</ul>"},"comments":{"edges":[]}},"pageContext":{"next":{"frontmatter":{"path":"/notes/free-aboutme-business-cards/","title":"My About.me profile","categories":["notes"],"tags":["design"]},"fileAbsolutePath":"/home/28041/opensource/github.com/mmistakes/made-mistakes-gatsby/src/posts/notes/free-aboutme-business-cards.md"},"previous":{"frontmatter":{"path":"/notes/record-art-review-agna-moraines-autobiography-7-inch/","title":"Agna Moraine's Autobiography, handwritten record art","categories":["notes"],"tags":["inspiration","design"]},"fileAbsolutePath":"/home/28041/opensource/github.com/mmistakes/made-mistakes-gatsby/src/posts/notes/record-art-review-agna-moraines-autobiography-7-inch.md"}}}}